#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:16
msgid ""
"The manual approval gate on the production backend prevents accidental "
"breakage of the service used by both the ACC CPSV Editor and the production "
"LDE frontend."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:20
msgid "Frontend deployment"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:22
msgid "The frontend builds to a static site. The workflow:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:24
msgid ""
"git push → GitHub Actions\n"
"  npm ci\n"
"  npm run build:acc     (ACC) / npm run build (production)\n"
"  Azure Static Web Apps deployment action\n"
"  Health check"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:32
msgid ""
"Build commands differ by environment because they inject different "
"`VITE_API_BASE_URL` values via `.env.acceptance` and `.env.production`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:34
msgid ""
"**ACC:** `https://acc.linkeddata.open-regels.nl` **Production:** `https://"
"linkeddata.open-regels.nl`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:37
msgid ""
"Azure Static Web Apps routing is configured in `staticwebapp.config.json` at "
"the repo root, handling SPA fallback and CORS headers for the static assets."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:41
msgid "Backend deployment"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:43
msgid ""
"The backend builds TypeScript and runs on Azure App Service (Linux, Node.js "
"22)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:45
msgid ""
"git push → GitHub Actions\n"
"  npm ci (backend package only)\n"
"  npm run build     (tsc → dist/)\n"
"  Azure Web Apps Deploy action\n"
"  POST-deployment: GET /v1/health → assert status \"healthy\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:53
msgid ""
"**ACC:** `https://acc.backend.linkeddata.open-regels.nl` **Production:** "
"`https://backend.linkeddata.open-regels.nl`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:58
msgid "Environment variables (Azure App Service)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:60
msgid ""
"Set via Azure CLI or the Azure portal. Key variables for each environment:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:62
msgid "**ACC:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:64
msgid ""
"az webapp config appsettings set \\\n"
"  --name ronl-linkeddata-backend-acc \\\n"
"  --resource-group RONL-Preproduction \\\n"
"  --settings \\\n"
"    NODE_ENV=acceptance \\\n"
"    PORT=8080 \\\n"
"    CORS_ORIGIN=\"https://acc.linkeddata.open-regels.nl,https://acc.cpsv-"
"editor.open-regels.nl\" \\\n"
"    TRIPLYDB_ENDPOINT=\"https://api.open-regels.triply.cc/...\" \\\n"
"    OPERATON_BASE_URL=\"https://operaton.open-regels.nl/engine-rest\" \\\n"
"    LOG_LEVEL=info"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:77
msgid "**Production:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:79
msgid ""
"az webapp config appsettings set \\\n"
"  --name ronl-linkeddata-backend-prod \\\n"
"  --resource-group RONL-Production \\\n"
"  --settings \\\n"
"    NODE_ENV=production \\\n"
"    PORT=8080 \\\n"
"    CORS_ORIGIN=\"https://linkeddata.open-regels.nl,https://cpsv-editor.open-"
"regels.nl\" \\\n"
"    TRIPLYDB_ENDPOINT=\"https://api.open-regels.triply.cc/...\" \\\n"
"    OPERATON_BASE_URL=\"https://operaton.open-regels.nl/engine-rest\" \\\n"
"    LOG_LEVEL=info"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:92
msgid ""
"`SCM_DO_BUILD_DURING_DEPLOYMENT=false` must be set on both App Service "
"instances — the build happens in GitHub Actions, not on Azure."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:96
msgid "Branch strategy"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:98
msgid ""
"feature/xyz  →  acc  →  main\n"
"                 ↓         ↓\n"
"               ACC       production\n"
"             (auto)      (auto frontend,\n"
"                          manual backend)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:106
msgid ""
"All changes go to `acc` first. After acceptance testing, merge `acc` → "
"`main` via a pull request. The production backend deployment then requires "
"manual approval in the GitHub Actions workflow."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:110
msgid "Post-deployment verification"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:112
msgid "After any deployment, verify:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:114
msgid ""
"# Backend health\n"
"curl https://backend.linkeddata.open-regels.nl/v1/health\n"
"\n"
"# Frontend loads\n"
"# Open https://linkeddata.open-regels.nl in browser\n"
"# Check Chain Builder loads DMNs\n"
"# Check no CORS errors in browser console"
msgstr ""
